{"tid":275995,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（討論）究竟養寵物係唔係一種差勁並且唔自然既行為","createTime":"2017-06-08T12:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T04:40:23.000Z","uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2595f4809fa5ff9ed5b27c9852455a3fc2a2f8e6","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"當以貓狗（常見）做例子<br />\n點解要做呢種自私既支配行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人食動物係大自然規律黎，係有必然性<br />\n但人養寵物（無必要）係一種我認為道德淪亡既行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.強加束縛&gt;帶狗帶狗繩<br />\n2.強制絕育&gt;口講為佢地好為佢地健康著想&hellip;但生殖器官比人剪左你估佢地想唔想<br />\n3.困佢地係屋企&gt;無自由<br />\n諗到再打<br />\n將上面個狗字變人字你地又接唔接受到呢"},{"pid":"8edf956a5ad927692824d15ffa5359a8e70f29b5","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"將心比己，你比人剪jj會點"},{"pid":"a4218e991a6c27acc55832fb56ddbf8e9923994f","tid":275995,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？"},{"pid":"4e8e746cd2f50658be0d861e9a461791d5fbb805","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"仲有叫d細路仔學養寵物培養愛心真係好<span style=\"color: red;\">嘔心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n培養佢地做控制狂支配隻寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當左自己係做主個個，而扭曲佢地既同理心，遲d大個左對其他人都會有一種支配而不平等既心態"},{"pid":"9fdceae2fb00a1208586384109d1e88203f6d5c5","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n咁點解養佢地就得，但唔可以食佢地呢？都係為左私利<br />\n但食佢地佢地就只會痛苦一時，養佢地就會痛苦一世"},{"pid":"8bf8e245a5f035d52ac43360ff2d5d71a76618db","tid":275995,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n咁點解養佢地就得，但唔可以食佢地呢？都係為左私利<br />\n但食佢地佢地就只會痛苦一時，養佢地就會痛苦一世</blockquote><br />\n因為養佢地會令佢地連痛苦係乜都唔記得 但係食佢地佢地會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a90da9e03b4df82b9cc8f5501f7686f85696bf4","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n咁點解養佢地就得，但唔可以食佢地呢？都係為左私利<br />\n但食佢地佢地就只會痛苦一時，養佢地就會痛苦一世</blockquote><br />\n因為養佢地會令佢地連痛苦係乜都唔記得 但係食佢地佢地會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14b40d57571ded9a0ddf7a708eb763b12b56ea4","tid":275995,"uid":46038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T02:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n咁點解養佢地就得，但唔可以食佢地呢？都係為左私利<br />\n但食佢地佢地就只會痛苦一時，養佢地就會痛苦一世</blockquote><br />\n因為養佢地會令佢地連痛苦係乜都唔記得 但係食佢地佢地會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我養隻狗而隻狗生活舒適過你，你點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a04f79e0e1ffd8e98707e6253186859a190c58f","tid":275995,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n咁點解養佢地就得，但唔可以食佢地呢？都係為左私利<br />\n但食佢地佢地就只會痛苦一時，養佢地就會痛苦一世</blockquote><br />\n因為養佢地會令佢地連痛苦係乜都唔記得 但係食佢地佢地會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我養隻狗而隻狗生活舒適過你，你點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好威呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2405a8ff0f81de09d84e95562848938aff2f42","tid":275995,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"係自私<br />\n所以先更加要好好咁對待佢地<br />\n<br />\n至於點解得貓狗地位先咁高<br />\n我諗單純係因為佢地已經被馴化同埋可以同養主有最多既交流<br />\n<br />\n當然有部分係覺得得意就養<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得養得寵物就係自私既行為<br />\n但人本來就係自私，所以咁樣並無不妥<br />\n<br />\n重點係養既過程有無好好咁對佢"},{"pid":"853edc5fa075ba04507ea87d7ceeac6d39ef8a82","tid":275995,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物本來就係人嘅私利 做乜？養寵物都要講大義？</blockquote><br />\n此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}